<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="165" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="2.[1345,2549,2841,3345]" pageId="2" pageNumber="165">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1345,1583,3195,3228]" pageId="2" pageNumber="165">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but the Manombo Woolly Lemur is nocturnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
